{
  "texts": [
    "Since our goal is to optimise balanced accuracy (the average of the sensitivity and specificity of the model (Kuhn et al., 2023)), we resample the training data to have the same number of positive and negative examples.",
    "There are however limitations to this approach:",
    "• There may be a substantial accuracy trade-off compared to the fairness-unaware model.",
    "• Access to the sensitive feature is required to train the \"fairness-unaware\" model in the first instance.",
    "An alternative to threshold optimisation is to perform a grid search, where multiple models are trained using different trade-off points between performance and fairness."
  ]
}